title: [Catacombs, Tunnels]
description: Oddly deformed mushrooms dot the rocky surface in this chamber.

Oddly deformed mushrooms dot the rocky surface in this chamber.  The horrid, ghastly-grey mushrooms are thin and flat in some places, while other sections appear ready to burst in a spray of viscid liquid.  Unlit torches adorn both sides of an opened doorway.
